  "design_notes": "The chart is built on consecutive, perfectly tiled phrases with zero gaps from bar 0 to 71. In S0 (high-energy intro), steps are moderately syncopated with holds on the melody to reflect the surprisingly intense vocal presence. S1 builds tension using a continuous stream of 8ths. S2 is the massive drop (chorus) featuring punchy jumps on major musical accents/downbeats, clear zigzags, and box movement parameters with light crossover tolerance. S3-S5 acts as a chilled wind-down, leading to a sparse, metronome-like fade-out in the S6 outro to maintain playability to the very end.",
